from_children_2019_s_green_food_producti.description:
For children’s education, food production and food consumption: on the elementary school ground, dig a hole for composting and other plots for year-round vegetable production. One of the plots could be for a seed bed of different vegetables production; one plot could be for a nursery containing different fruits and timber plants; and one plot could be for local vegetable seed production. Motivate the community and demonstrate how to grow food on the rooftops andgrow balcony gardens. &#13;
