is_it_a_chance_or_the_treatment_reality_.description:
Smart, educational reality TV, 'The Chance', suspensefully matches donors with donees. Upliftingly, everyone finds a match.&#13;
&#13;
But we soon see that in real life not everyone does - yet&#13;
&#13;
...donation shouldn't be 'A Chance', it should be 'The Treatment'&#13;

